pitality and the toleration of difference.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aHomeless persons. 0aHomelessnessxGovernment policy. 0aHomelessness. 4aCultural Studies : Identity. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 4aSociology : Urban Sociology. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / Urban.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791484937423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791484937/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles